hanistan in Your hand."},{"s":13.42,"e":16.08,"text":"Kabul crying, Kandahar sighing,"},{"s":17.24,"e":19.88,"text":"Herat hungry, mothers trying."},{"s":21.44,"e":24.08,"text":"Bread is thin and prices rise,"},{"s":24.74,"e":26.52,"text":"Children search with tired eyes."},{"s":27.54,"e":30.08,"text":"Seventeen million need relief,"},{"s":31.2,"e":33.62,"text":"Turn their hunger into peace."},{"s":35.12,"e":36.88,"text":"Three-point-seven million small,"},{"s":38.46,"e":40.68,"text":"Need Your healing, hear them all."},{"s":41.54,"e":43.44,"text":"Malnutrition, cold condition,"},{"s":44.94,"e":46.8,"text":"Meet their need with swift provision."},{"s":46.8,"e":50.28,"text":"For the girls denied the page,"},{"s":50.56,"e":52.06,"text":"Open schools and break the cage."},{"s":52.14,"e":53.84,"text":"Books and dreams and futures bright,"},{"s":53.86,"e":55.56,"text":"Bring them learning, bring them light."},{"s":55.56,"e":57.34,"text":"For the women trained to heal,"},{"s":57.58,"e":59.02,"text":"Guard their skill and make it real."},{"s":59.18,"e":61.38,"text":"Teachers, nurses, midwives, wise,"},{"s":61.44,"e":63.06,"text":"Keep their calling, let them rise."},{"s":63.44,"e":65.14,"text":"For returnees at the gate,"},{"s":65.36,"e":67.8,"text":"No work, no roof, no food, no plate—"},{"s":67.92,"e":69.56,"text":"Give them shelter, give them rest,"},{"s":69.96,"e":71.34,"text":"Guide the wounded, bless the stressed."},{"s":71.46,"e":73.22,"text":"For the poor with empty hands,"},{"s":73.46,"e":74.98,"text":"Raise up mercy through all lands."},{"s":75.02,"e":76.6,"text":"For the sick, disabled, weak,"},{"s":76.84,"e":78.3,"text":"Be the strength they cannot speak."},{"s":78.68,"e":80.42,"text":"End the fear and end the fighting,"},{"s":80.42,"e":82.26,"text":"Send the rain and send the writing."},{"s":82.26,"e":83.62,"text":"Fields with grain and hearts with grace,"},{"s":83.62,"e":85.5,"text":"Peace in every province, place."},{"s":85.78,"e":87.34,"text":"Let no child be lost to pain,"},{"s":87.42,"e":89.06,"text":"Let no prayer fall down in vain."},{"s":89.42,"e":92.26,"text":"Allah, Lord, Most Merciful One,"},{"s":94.12,"e":95.8,"text":"Warm the night and raise the sun."},{"s":97.76,"e":99.28,"text":"Feed the hungry, free the bound,"},{"s":100.82,"e":104.1,"text":"Lift the fallen from the ground."},{"s":105.48,"e":108.4,"text":"Afghanistan, through dust and flame,"},{"s":108.6,"e":112.32,"text":"May hope come home and bless your name."}],"duration":116.84,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.302Z","stats":{"whisperWords":251,"polishedWords":230,"matched":190,"matchRate":0.826}}